Use syncthing to sync files between mac and windows

install syncthing on both windows and mac

open syncthing in mac in browser and in standalone app in windows

Setup

1. Do the following on MAC

click on "Actions" and select "show id"
Copy the uuid shown in the popup

2. Now goto windows machine

In the main window, click on "Add Remote Device" under remote devices section
Enter the ID copied in the first step in the "Device ID" box .
Configure the remaining things like name, refresh interval and the default sharing folders.


3. Now do the vice versa to add windows machine in mac
